# ── Generated native platform folders ───────────────────────────────────────
# android/ and ios/ are regenerated by `tool/bootstrap.sh` (flutter create) and
# then patched with tool/apply_platform_overlays.py — not committed. This keeps
# binary blobs (gradle-wrapper.jar, Xcode project) and package-name drift out of
# the repo. See README "Bootstrap".
/android/
/ios/
/linux/
/macos/
/windows/
/web/

